#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:168
msgid ""
"- Check \"Attempt to remove the driver for this device\", and hit uninstall"
msgstr "- 选中“尝试删除此设备的驱动程序”然后点击卸载"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:166
msgid ""
"- If want to uninstall driver, uninstall virtual network adapter until there "
"is only one remains, go to Device manager - Network adapters, right click on "
"\"TAP - Win32 Adapter V9\" and choose \"Uninstall device\""
msgstr ""
"- 如果想要卸载驱动，先卸载虚拟网卡直到只剩下1个，到设备管理器 - 网络适配器，"
"在“TAP - Win32 Adapter V9”上右键并选择“卸载设备”"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:170
msgid ""
"- If you accidentally uninstalled all virtual network adapter, click on "
"\"Install new\" to add one, in order to uninstall driver in device manager"
msgstr ""
"- 如果不小心卸载了所有虚拟网卡，点击“新安装”来添加一个，就可以在设备管理器中"
"卸载驱动"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:156
msgid ""
"- If you denied driver installation and don't want to install driver, go to "
"Device Manager - Network adapters, right click on \"Unknown device\" and "
"choose \"Uninstall device\""
msgstr ""
"- 如果你拒绝驱动安装并且不想安装驱动，到设备管理器 - 网络适配器，右键“未知设"
"备”并选择“卸载设备”"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:154
msgid ""
"- If you still want to install driver, click on \"Install new\" again and "
"agree, then you will have two virtual network adapter, one might be "
"redundant and need to be uninstalled manually"
msgstr ""
"- 如果还是想安装驱动，点击“新安装”并同意，这种情况下会有两个虚拟网卡，其中一"
"个可能是多余的并且需要手动卸载"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:161
msgid ""
"- Try click on \"Refresh\" button until textbox shows virtual network "
"adapter name with green background"
msgstr "- 尝试点击“刷新”按钮直到文本框中显示虚拟网卡名称以及绿色背景"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:176
msgid "About virtual network adapter"
msgstr "关于虚拟网卡"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:152
msgid ""
"Although you can deny it, but device will still add to system, and show as "
"\"Unknown device\""
msgstr "即使你可以拒绝，设备仍然会添加到系统，并且显示为“未知设备”"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:293
#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:345
msgid "Can't confirm what happened, the raw error message is"
msgstr "不能确认发生了什么，原始错误信息是"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:49
msgid "Close"
msgstr "关闭"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:313
msgid "Confirm?"
msgstr "确定？"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:249
msgid "Detected exist virtual network adapter"
msgstr "检测到已安装的虚拟网卡"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:28
msgid "Detected virtual network adapter"
msgstr "检测到的虚拟网卡"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:288
msgid "Device has configured, but you cancelled driver installation dialog"
msgstr "设备已添加，但你拒绝了驱动安装确认对话框"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:331
msgid "Didn't find any adapter on your system"
msgstr "未在系统上找到任何虚拟网卡"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:275
#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:340
msgid "Driver files incomplete, "
msgstr "驱动文件不完整， "

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:26
msgid "Help"
msgstr "帮助"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:149
msgid ""
"If you don't want to install driver, don't click on \"Install new\" button"
msgstr "如果不想安装驱动，不要点击“新安装”按钮"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:289
msgid ""
"In this case, you need to uninstall redundant virtual network adapter once "
"any other install successfully"
msgstr "在这种情况下，你需要在任何其他安装请求成功后卸载多余的虚拟网卡"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:272
msgid "Install adapter failed:"
msgstr "虚拟网卡安装失败："

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:249
msgid "Install another one?"
msgstr "再安装另一个？"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:32
msgid "Install new"
msgstr "新安装"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:159
msgid "Installed virtual adapter may not be detected immediately"
msgstr "已安装的虚拟网卡可能不会立刻被检测到"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:12
#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:31
msgid "Manage virtual network adapter"
msgstr "管理虚拟网卡"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:239
msgid "Metric has set"
msgstr "跃点数（metric）已设置"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:43
#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:123
msgid "Open device manager"
msgstr "打开设备管理器"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:290
msgid ""
"Or go to device manager and uninstall \"Unknown device\" if you don't want "
"to have a virtual network adapter"
msgstr "或是如果你不想要虚拟网卡，到设备管理器卸载“未知设备”"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:47
msgid "Refresh"
msgstr "刷新"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:45
msgid "Rename"
msgstr "重命名"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:204
msgid ""
"Select network adapter in opened window, press F2 to rename\n"
"Click on Refresh button after you are done"
msgstr ""
"在新打开的窗口中选择网卡，按F2进行重命名\n"
"完成后点击刷新按钮"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:34
msgid "Set metric"
msgstr "设置跃点数（metric）"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:268
msgid "Successfully installed new adapter"
msgstr "成功安装新网卡"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:324
msgid "Successfully uninstalled adapter"
msgstr "成功卸载网卡"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:258
msgid "Suggest read help before install first virtual network adapter"
msgstr "首次安装虚拟网卡前建议阅读帮助"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:337
msgid "Target adapter doesn't exist on your system"
msgstr "目标网卡在你的系统上不存在"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:173
msgid ""
"Tinc game can not identify which virtual network adapter is installed by "
"Tinc game, or installed by other program, thus you must take control of the "
"uninstall process"
msgstr ""
"Tinc网络不能验证哪个虚拟网卡是被Tinc网络安装的，或是被其他软件安装的，因此必"
"须由你控制卸载过程"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:37
msgid "Uninstall"
msgstr "卸载"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:328
msgid "Uninstall adapter failed:"
msgstr "卸载网卡失败："

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:164
msgid "Uninstall button is not uninstall driver button"
msgstr "卸载按钮不是卸载驱动按钮"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:313
msgid "Uninstalling last virtual network adapter"
msgstr "正在卸载最后一个虚拟网卡"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:284
msgid "You may need to run tinc game as admin"
msgstr "你应该以管理员权限运行tinc网络"

#: src/Frame/ManageTap/ManageTapFrame.cpp:334
msgid "You need to run tinc game as admin"
msgstr "你需要以管理员权限运行tinc网络"

